{"word":"ἀντιγράφω","slug":"ἀντιγράφω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀντιγράφω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to write against</i> or <i>in answer, write back</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>, as law-term, <i>to put in as a plea, to plead against</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}